I am going to make a quiz app
in which i will add different topics for quiz
and user will be able to select the topic and then the quiz will start
each question have a certain time limit after which the question will move to the next question
the time limit can be set by the user

Requirements =========>>>
1. User can select the topic.
2. User can set the time limit for each question.
3. each time new questions will be generated at random. 
4. User can see the score and time remaining for each question.
5. user can see the rank on the leaderboard (on individual topics).
6. user can see the overall rank on the leaderboard.
7. user can see the questions and answers in the history section with time taken to answer each question.
8. badges earned.
